{
  "stem": "18626.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we have the same right to live.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it didn't-- it didn't come so fast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That even old Gentile people with crosses wearing, they still hated Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR  SECONDS] That's right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And to say the truth, you know, it was very hard to make friends with Lithuanians.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Even if they are friendly with you on the outside, but in-- in their hearts, they were not friends.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's [?why?] when they made the pograms, and the Germans were already you know it was a free city, Kaunas in Slobodka.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The Russians were already escaping, you know, chasing away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because the Germans came in with such a power, they bombed the airfields.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the Russians, the soldiers were not organized no more.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They didn't see the officers anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was a chaos in the-- in the Soviet army because of the speed of Hitler's war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was so organized that they were off balanced.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the Lithuanians right away took that for a good opportunity to start killing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So before even the Germans marched in, and it was almost like a free city, you know, only a couple of Russian soldiers who got lost didn't know where to run.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were confused.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They had ?] no officers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The Lithuanians though saw how they-- they killed them, the-- the Soviet army soldiers, the Russians.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So you see how the hatred worked against.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And when the Germans were all heading to Lithuanian, they didn't tell the Lithuanians, go kill the Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They did it by them self, happy, And they did the first pograms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they killed thousand Jews in Slobodka.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] With knives and ax, they knocked off people's Jewish heads.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother went to a bakery.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
